criteria.driver_alignment:
Represent — defined the planned output (incremental cash flow schedule) that guided implementation;  
Implement — executed the plan with specific, traceable cash flow entries and metric calculations (initial outlay, depreciation, terminal flows, NPV/IRR/PI/payback);  
Validate — explicitly checked that discounting and metric placement matched the plan;  
Evolve — ran systematic scenario analyses (20% revenue drop, WACC ±2%) demonstrating continued, methodical execution.
